| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2020-0133 — Recovery Inhibition (netwalker)"
| comment "Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: ca25a36c-a09c-5ded-8cd5-c444b4be3b0a"
